parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause unexpected deployment, leading to distraction, reduced visibility, and increased risk of accidents, or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially resulting in serious injury or fatalities.
symptoms: Unexpected airbag deployment
loud explosion
puff of white smoky powder filling the car cabin
reduced visibility
failure of airbag to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning ABS can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The ABS pump activates continuously
even when the vehicle is stationary
the steering wheel shakes vigorously when applying brakes
loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal vibration can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The steering wheel shakes vigorously when applying brakes
the brake pedal vibrates or pulses when pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to properly diagnose and repair ABS issues after an accident can lead to continued safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The ABS system malfunctions or fails to function properly after an accident
the ABS pump activates continuously
even when the vehicle is stationary.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Leading to Vehicle Fire
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause a vehicle fire, which can lead to serious accidents, injuries, or even fatalities. It can also result in significant damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
symptoms: Loud cracking or unusual sounds from the engine
sudden loss of engine power
engine stalling or failure
smoke or flames emanating from the engine compartment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden engine failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, especially if the failure occurs at high speeds.
symptoms: Loud cracking or unusual sounds from the engine
sudden loss of engine power
engine stalling or failure
inability to restart the engine.
